<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>To-Label - room</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/uploads/To-Label.png" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      integrity="sha384-rbsA2VBKQhggwzxH7pPCaAqO46MgnOM80zW1RWuH61DGLwZJEdK2Kadq2F9CUG65"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-OERcA2EqjJCMA+/3y+gxIOqMEjwtxJY7qPCqsdltbNJuaOe923+mo//f6V8Qbsw3"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/vue/dist/vue.js"></script>
    <script
      src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.0.js"
      integrity="sha256-JlqSTELeR4TLqP0OG9dxM7yDPqX1ox/HfgiSLBj8+kM="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.3/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

    <!-- Japanese Font -->
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      /* For iPad mini and larger devices */

      body {
        font-family: "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;
        background-color: white;
        color: black;
      }

      @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .navbar-nav .dropdown-menu {
          display: block;
          position: static;
          background-color: transparent;
          border: 0;
          box-shadow: none;
        }

        .navbar-nav .dropdown-item {
          padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
        }

        .navbar-nav .nav-link {
          display: inline;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="container" style="background-color: rgb(249, 245, 253)">
    <!-- header -->

    <nav
      class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark"
      style="position: fixed; left: 0; top: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 100"
    >
      <div class="container">
        <a
          class="navbar-brand"
          href="/home"
          style="
            font-size: 3vh;
            font-weight: bold;
            position: relative;
            left: -5%;
          "
          >To-Label</a
        >
        <button
          class="navbar-toggler"
          type="button"
          data-bs-toggle="collapse"
          data-bs-target="#navbarNav"
          aria-controls="navbarNav"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-label="Toggle navigation"
          style="height: 4vh; width: 4vh; position: relative; right: -5%"
        >
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon" style="font-size: 2vh"></span>
        </button>
        <div
          class="collapse navbar-collapse justify-content-end"
          style="margin: 2vh"
          id="navbarNav"
        >
          <!-- Mobile version menu -->
          <ul class="navbar-nav d-lg-none">
            <li class="nav-item dropdown" style="height: 3vh">
              <ul
                class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-end bg-dark"
                aria-labelledby="navbarDropdown"
              >
                <li>
                  <a
                    class="dropdown-item text-white"
                    href="/history"
                    style="font-size: 3vh; font-weight: bold"
                    >History</a
                  >
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a
                    class="dropdown-item text-white"
                    href="/setting"
                    style="font-size: 3vh; font-weight: bold"
                    >Setting</a
                  >
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a
                    class="dropdown-item text-white"
                    href="/help"
                    style="font-size: 3vh; font-weight: bold"
                    >Help</a
                  >
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a
                    class="dropdown-item text-white"
                    href="/logout"
                    style="font-size: 3vh; font-weight: bold"
                    >Logout</a
                  >
                </li>
              </ul>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <!-- Desktop version menu -->
          <ul class="navbar-nav d-none d-lg-flex">
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a
                class="nav-link"
                href="/history"
                style="font-size: 3vh; font-weight: bold"
                >History</a
              >
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a
                class="nav-link"
                href="/setting"
                style="font-size: 3vh; font-weight: bold"
                >Setting</a
              >
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a
                class="nav-link"
                href="/help"
                style="font-size: 3vh; font-weight: bold"
                >Help</a
              >
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a
                class="nav-link"
                href="/logout"
                style="font-size: 3vh; font-weight: bold"
                >Logout</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <main
      class="container"
      style="position: absolute; top: 18vh; width: 100%; z-index: -100"
    >
      <div class="card p-5">
        <h3 class="text-center pb-3">レッテルの結果</h3>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header"><%= username %></div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <% your_msg_list.forEach(element =>{%>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header"><%= element.from_username %></div>
              <div class="card-body"><%= element.msg %></div>
            </div>
            <% }) %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% other_msg_list.forEach(element=>{%>
        <div class="card mt-4">
          <div class="card-header"><%= element[0] %></div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <% element[1].forEach(child=>{%>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header"><%= child.from_username %></div>
              <div class="card-body"><%= child.msg %></div>
            </div>
            <%})%>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-5">
          この部屋は、1日経つと削除されて、アクセスできなくなります。明日以降は、ユーザーのプロフィールページより閲覧ください。
        </p>
        <%})%>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
